data.description: Price reduction! Welcome home, you could be in by the end of the year. Three spacious finished levels for your enjoyment. As you walk into the foyer entrance onto engineered wood flooring, you will head straight back to the lower-level bedroom with a fully appointed bathroom, which includes a single vanity with a stand-up tiled shower. Access to the 1-car garage with remote from this level also. As you take the stairs to the second level, you will find a dining room, an open kitchen with an island, granite counter tops, S/S appliances, tile on the wall and back splash. Crown molding is an added touch throughout the second level. The family room is very spacious with speakers installed in the ceiling; half bath has been completely remodeled with shutters on the window. Sliding doors take you outside to the maintenance free deck with vinyl railing that backs up to trees. This area will allow you to spend quiet evenings with family and friends, ideal for outdoor dining and grilling. The third level is where you will find the primary bedroom and bathroom, complete with a double vanity, and tub with shower. This level also has a laundry closet and a 3rd bedroom and full bath, both bedrooms on this level have walk in closets. Conveniently located near the neighborhood play area, walking paths, and the community pool and clubhouse that you may reserve for special events. This Townhome is close to the elementary school. You will find many dining and shopping options just a short drive away.
